Functions that return data range with data from the rows in range rng (if parameter targetCol=0), where certain criteria is satisfied in in column col, 
or 
functions that return an array with data from the cells in range rng (if parameter targetCol is specified), where certain criteria is satisfied in in column col:

whenCellEmpty(rng, col, targetCol = 0)
whenCellNotEmpty(rng, col, targetCol = 0)
whenDateAfter(date, rng, col, targetCol = 0)
whenDateBefore(date, rng, col, targetCol = 0)
whenDateEqualTo(date, rng, col, targetCol = 0)
whenDateEqualToAny(dateArr, rng, col, targetCol = 0)
whenDateNotEqualTo(date, rng, col, targetCol = 0)
whenDateNotEqualToAny(dateArr, rng, col, targetCol = 0)
whenNumberBetween(start, end, rng, col, targetCol = 0)
whenNumberEqualTo(number, rng, col, targetCol = 0)
whenNumberEqualToAny(numberArr, rng, col, targetCol = 0)
whenNumberGreaterThan(number, rng, col, targetCol = 0)
whenNumberGreaterThanOrEqualTo(number, rng, col, targetCol = 0)
whenNumberLessThan(number, rng, col, targetCol = 0)
whenNumberLessThanOrEqualTo(number, rng, col, targetCol = 0)
whenNumberNotBetween(start, end, rng, col, targetCol = 0)
whenNumberNotEqualTo(number, rng, col, targetCol = 0)
whenNumberNotEqualToAny(numberArr, rng, col, targetCol = 0)
whenTextContains(txt, rng, col, targetCol = 0)
whenTextDoesNotContain(txt, rng, col, targetCol = 0)
whenTextEndsWith(txt, rng, col, targetCol = 0)
whenTextEqualTo(txt, rng, col, targetCol = 0)
whenTextEqualToAny(textArr, rng, col, targetCol = 0)
whenTextNotEqualTo(txt, rng, col, targetCol = 0)
whenTextNotEqualToAny(textArr, rng, col, targetCol = 0)
whenTextStartsWith(txt, rng, col, targetCol = 0)
whenTrimmedCellEmpty(rng, col, targetCol = 0)
whenTrimmedTextEndsWith(txt, rng, col, targetCol = 0)



Functions that return array with row numbers inside range rng, where certain criteria is satisfied in in column col:

rowsWhereCellEmpty(rng, col)
rowsWhereCellNotEmpty(rng, col)
rowsWhereDateAfter(date, rng, col)
rowsWhereDateBefore(date, rng, col)
rowsWhereDateEqualTo(date, rng, col)
rowsWhereDateEqualToAny(dateArr, rng, col)
rowsWhereDateNotEqualTo(date, rng, col)
rowsWhereDateNotEqualToAny(dateArr, rng, col)
rowsWhereNumberBetween(start, end, rng, col)
rowsWhereNumberEqualTo(number, rng, col)
rowsWhereNumberEqualToAny(numberArr, rng, col)
rowsWhereNumberGreaterThan(number, rng, col)
rowsWhereNumberGreaterThanOrEqualTo(number, rng, col)
rowsWhereNumberLessThan(number, rng, col)
rowsWhereNumberLessThanOrEqualTo(number, rng, col)
rowsWhereNumberNotBetween(start, end, rng, col)
rowsWhereNumberNotEqualTo(number, rng, col)
rowsWhereNumberNotEqualToAny(numberArr, rng, col)
rowsWhereTextContains(txt, rng, col)
rowsWhereTextDoesNotContain(txt, rng, col)
rowsWhereTextEndsWith(txt, rng, col)
rowsWhereTextEqualTo(txt, rng, col)
rowsWhereTextEqualToAny(textArr, rng, col)
rowsWhereTextNotEqualTo(txt, rng, col)
rowsWhereTextNotEqualToAny(textArr, rng, col)
rowsWhereTextStartsWith(txt, rng, col)
rowsWhereTrimmedCellEmpty(rng, col)
rowsWhereTrimmedTextEndsWith(txt, rng, col)
